    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/460d5ac15cd4bb395e839436c92491d7.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/3d0d42fd604cdcf7a48038376789b5b0.poster.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/3d0d42fd604cdcf7a48038376789b5b0.webm?t=1769642928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/3d0d42fd604cdcf7a48038376789b5b0.mp4?t=1769642928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >千禧年在即，塔恩拉的世界即将迎来一场绝世阴谋。在经历了战火连绵、腥风血雨的继位战争之后，维尔迪亚帝国民不聊生、满目疮痍。随着女皇芙洛里娜的登基，这场恶性循环似乎终于被打破。不料，一名将军集结大军，公然宣叛，还在首都掳走了女皇。你，一名军校毕业生，将带领部队讨伐逆贼……而这场战争即将在这片大陆上拉开惊天动地大事件的序幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2D策略型回合制角色扮演游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 率领小队作战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 故事内容丰富，30-40小时的战役流程，重玩性高 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 50+可选角色职业 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 深度战略游戏，边玩边学，容易上手</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 角色和军队设置拥有无限可能性</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/dbe92bc08130bb712229482001379f3f.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/377325b3ca12030b362b7a364fb710ef.poster.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/377325b3ca12030b362b7a364fb710ef.webm?t=1769642928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/377325b3ca12030b362b7a364fb710ef.mp4?t=1769642928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法着重于大规模作战，布局智取敌人。队伍拼杀将自动进行，只需观赏并等待结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 操控部队（至多9人）作战，通过抢占高地、扼据要冲、树林埋伏等方式赢得上风</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 注意天气变化，或是被突如其来的暴风雪或热浪击倒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过解放城镇、占领资源点来提升声誉，壮大军队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 瓦解敌方战意，鼓舞我军士气</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 消灭敌军队长，打击敌方指挥</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/37c562b66c5c75467e68af0a53442e7e.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/6fd991a2606d8aa4ef498b405e88ce03.poster.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/6fd991a2606d8aa4ef498b405e88ce03.webm?t=1769642928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/6fd991a2606d8aa4ef498b405e88ce03.mp4?t=1769642928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术赢得战斗。战略赢得战争。尘埃落尽之后，是时候收治伤员，集结部队，展开另一场大战，一步一步将和平带回塔恩拉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 超过50种职业可供组建部队，包括重步兵、弓兵、冲击骑兵、医疗兵、火枪兵、龙、战斗法师等</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 为部队装备通过战斗赢得的道具和神器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 将新兵训练成精英战士，或招募佣兵来立即提升军队战力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 研发阵营的科技树，升级职业，增强战斗部队</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/18e26d0cdc2d336374990f886b0a0d8b.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/ebff7647e59115208ce8d98b9163a975.poster.avif?t=1769642928\" width=600 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488200/extras/ebff7647e59115208ce8d98b9163a975.webm?t=1769642928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帝国战争学院的毕业生被迅速派出镇压叛乱，却卷入了一场出乎意料的可怕阴谋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 结交来自各个阵营的伙伴、英雄、盟友和对手</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 体验动态关系系统，解锁独特对话，建立情比金坚的关系，获得角色的强力加成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在这片和平岌岌可危的塔恩拉大陆，体验暗藏杀机、背信弃义、豪情壮志的史诗故事</p></li></ul>",
